   Trade Figures
   For April Show
   Narrowed Gap
   ---
   Deficit Totaled $6.94 Billion
   Following Sharp Decline
   In Imports to the U.S.
   ----
   By Tuesday Georges
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
